<div class="main-container">
  <div class="banner image-fit">
    <div class="font-container">
      <h2 class="tag-line">A hero for every moment</h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cards-container">
    <div class="homepage-cards">
      <h1>Find your hero</h1>
      <p>Improve every situation with a hero by your side</p>
      <%= link_to heros_path do  %>
       <button class="btn button-discover-red">See all heroes</button>
      <% end %>
     </div>
  </div>
<!--     <h2 class="text-center">A hero by your side makes every moment better</h2> -->
  <div class="full-home-feelings-banner"></div>
  <div class="container how-to-become-a-hero">
    <h1 class="text-center pb-5">How to become a hero</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="d-flex">
        <div class="col-4 text-center mr-4">
          <div>
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dtulzuk5j/image/upload/v1605794927/pexels-andrea-piacquadio-874242_rngiyu.jpg" class="how-to-image">
          </div>
          <h3>Define your power</h3>
          <p>All heroes start with a power. Think about how your power will come in handy. When you have an idea, <%= link_to "start the submission process", new_hero_path %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-4 text-center">
          <div>
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dtulzuk5j/image/upload/v1605794924/Screenshot_2020-11-19_at_14.41.13_wa3ril.png" class="how-to-image">
          </div>
          <h3>Share your services</h3>
          <p>Next, you'll need to describe the service you will provide with your superpower. Find the right title, share the value of what youâ€™re offering in detail, give it a fair price and set your availability for when it makes sense.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-4 text-center ml-4">
          <div>
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dtulzuk5j/image/upload/v1605794920/Screenshot_2020-11-19_at_14.47.56_nkieju.png" class="how-to-image">
          </div>
          <h3>Submit your hero</h3>
          <p>You're almost there! Make sure to put in all the right information and click on Create Hero. Go on the main page and see that your hero has been added.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center pt-5">
      <%= link_to new_hero_path do  %>
      <button class="btn button-discover-red">Become a hero</button>
    <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h1 class="text-center heros-title">Some of our heroes</h1>
  <div class="container heros-home-display">
    <div class="cards-home row justify-content-center">
      <% @heros.each do |hero| %>
        <%  if hero.bookings.empty? %>
          <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3 m-3 card-hero-home">
            <% if hero.photo.attached? %>
              <%= cl_image_tag hero.photo.key, height: 300, width: 400, crop: :fill %>
            <% end %>
            <div class="card-hero-infos-home py-3 px-2">
              <h1><%= link_to hero.title, hero_path(hero) %></h1>
              <p><%= hero.superpower %></p>
              <button class="btn btn-book">About us</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center pt-5">
    <%= link_to heros_path do  %>
     <button class="btn button-discover-red">See all heroes</button>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
